      "lang": "javascript",
      "content": "function soma(a, b) {\n  return a + b;\n}\n\nfunction semReturn() {\n  const x = 10;\n  // sem return\n}\n\nconsole.log(soma(2, 3));     // 5\nconsole.log(semReturn());    // undefined",
